<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Chat2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Chat,</orth> vb., to prate: <bibl n="shak. err 2.2.27" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. II, 2, 27</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. shr 3.2.123" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. III, 2, 123</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. shr 5.2.11" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 2, 11</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 4.4.26" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. IV, 4, 26</bibl>. Transitively: <cit><quote>your prattling nurse into a rapture lets her baby cry while she --s him,</quote> <bibl n="shak. cor 2.1.224" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. II, 1, 224</bibl></cit> (cf. <emph>speak</emph>), == of him.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>